item.title: CVE-2023-0956|2023-08-03T18:08:13.924Z -- tel-ster -- telwin%20scada%20webinterface
item.description: External input could be used on TEL-STER TelWin SCADA WebInterface to construct paths to files and directories without properly neutralizing special elements within the pathname, which could allow an unauthenticated attacker to read files on the system.
